Django Setty is a Django app which allows users to configure settings dynamically in the Django Admin console. A number of data types are supported - dicts, lists, integers, floats, strings and booleans. Two backends are bundled - one is a database backend which uses the database to retrieve the settings, and the other uses Memcached to cache the settings defined in the database.


